                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 inline-block ring-4 ring-emerald-500/20"></span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">Volume Tinggi (1.000+)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 inline-block ring-4 ring-indigo-500/20"></span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">Volume Sedang (500 - 999)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-rose-500 inline-block ring-4 ring-amber-500/20"></span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">Volume Rendah (&lt; 500)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-1.5 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 text-[10px] text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">
                        *Ukuran lingkaran membesar secara logaritmik berdasarkan jumlah peserta (Rentang 1 - 10.000).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

